import org.apache.spark.sql.types._

val schema =  StructType(
                        Array(
                          StructField("dt", TimestampType,false),
                          StructField("lat", DoubleType,false),
                          StructField("lon", DoubleType,false),
                          StructField("base", StringType,false)
                        )
                      )
                  
//  File location and type
val file_location = "file:///home/pal/UberData/Jan2014-June2014/*.csv"
val file_type = "csv"

//  CSV options
val infer_schema = "false"
val first_row_is_header = "true"
val delimiter = ","

//  The applied options are for CSV files. For other file types, these will be ignored.
val df = (spark.read.format(file_type) 
          .option("inferSchema", infer_schema) 
          .option("header", first_row_is_header) 
          .schema(schema)
          .option("timestampFormat","MM/dd/yyyy HH:mm:ss")
          .option("sep", delimiter) 
          .load(file_location)
          )
          
// Create a view or table

val temp_table_name = "uber_raw_data_2014_csv"

df.createOrReplaceTempView(temp_table_name)

import org.apache.spark.ml.feature.VectorAssembler
val featureCols = Array("lat", "lon")
val assembler = (new VectorAssembler()
                                .setInputCols(featureCols)
                                .setOutputCol("features")
                )


import org.apache.spark.ml.clustering.KMeans
val kmeans = (new KMeans()
                .setK(10)
                .setSeed(1L)
                .setFeaturesCol(assembler.getOutputCol)
                .setPredictionCol("cid")
                .setMaxIter(20)
                )

                
import org.apache.spark.ml.{Pipeline, PipelineModel}
val pipeline = (new Pipeline()
                  .setStages(Array(assembler, kmeans))
                )


// Fit the pipeline to training documents.
val pipelineModel = pipeline.fit(df)
var final_df_2014 = pipelineModel.transform(df)

%cassandra
CREATE TABLE taxidata.uber (
    cid int,
    dt timestamp,
    base text,
    features text,
    lat double,
    lon double,
    PRIMARY KEY (cid, dt, base, features)
) WITH CLUSTERING ORDER BY (dt ASC, base ASC, features ASC)
    AND bloom_filter_fp_chance = 0.01
    AND caching = {'keys': 'ALL', 'rows_per_partition': 'ALL'}
    AND comment = ''
    AND compaction = {'class': 'SizeTieredCompactionStrategy'}
    AND compression = {}
    AND crc_check_chance = 1.0
    AND dclocal_read_repair_chance = 0.1
    AND default_time_to_live = 0
    AND gc_grace_seconds = 864000
    AND max_index_interval = 2048
    AND memtable_flush_period_in_ms = 0
    AND min_index_interval = 128
    AND read_repair_chance = 0.0
    AND speculative_retry = '99.0PERCENTILE';

                (message:String) => ParseUber(message))
